reviews.review_text: knickerkicker Dear God in heaven, Jerry  repeated a verse, Joking, joking I see a lot of that " they messed up a verse " this can't be a good show, what a bunch of bologna. This is a solid show I don't give a rats ass what anyone says. Albany lacked traditional partying areas and the five o were among the top ballbusters. But the shows did not lack. Good karma to all G.D family
